:{{DIcon}} How have things been?
::'''Wallace:''' Ack, don't mention it.
::'''Wallace:''' A few days ago, I spent a small sum of money &mdash; as much as the price of a few antique vases. I requested for someone to fetch a mech-pet from the Underworld. Unfortunately... once it was assembled, it was nothing special.
::'''Wallace:''' As for the people who come from below, all they talk about is policies, money, and business. There is absolutely nothing I can talk to them about. How painfully mundane!
::'''Wallace:''' I just can't even fathom the point. Can you try to explain to me what's the use of money? How can people spend all day longing after something like this? It's so unrefined, down right vulgar even...
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
