:{{DIcon}} Made any new friends?
::'''Wallace:''' You know me, I have high standards for friends. Status, appearance, profession, eloquence... I don't compromise.
::'''Wallace:''' Knowing Regin is a stroke of luck, hard to find another friend as exceptional as him.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You've been fooled by Regin.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504049005-->
:::'''Wallace:''' Are you talking about my investment in ''Citizen Science''?
:::'''Wallace:''' I know it's a long shot, but when it comes to friends, money shouldn't matter. Plus, I'm not exactly short on cash.
:::'''Wallace:''' What I appreciate is his commitment. Regin has been diligently advocating his "big universe time tunnel" theory for years. If I can support him, why not?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Maybe try expanding your social circle.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504049009-->
:::'''Wallace:''' Belobog isn't that large, I practically know everyone in the Overworld area by now.
:::'''Wallace:''' I heard the Underworld area is getting safer by the day, maybe I'll visit someday. However, the locals seem pretty rough around the edges, probably not the ideal friend material for me.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504049011-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504049011-->
::'''Wallace:''' It's funny how friendship works. I had you scout out so many people, and yet no one wanted to be my friend.
::'''Wallace:''' Just when I was about to give up, I met Regin, maybe it was meant to be.
